## What this kit does NOT do (the deliberate manual step)
`{{GENERATOR}}` stamped the **blank** board and the **seed** decks. It did **not** author the
`<<TOKEN>>` business values, did **not** run the export, and did **not** inject
`{{APPROVAL_TOKEN_VAR}}`. Those are the FDE's supervised, per-customer acts (Phases 2–4) — the
CLI never authors business logic or holds a live credential.
